{"tid":1630470,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[長期置頂]核彈集中PO 跪求幫推 好重要","createTime":"2019-10-06T12:37:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T12:50:01.000Z","uid":238467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ead575289a8c535994f686db34be2b4e66e65874","tid":1630470,"uid":238467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:37:07.000Z","msg":"自從6月9號開始<br />\n大家都識講核彈核彈 重點重點<br />\n但係每次都係hold一兩日就算<br />\n咁樣真係核彈咩？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開始嗰啲搵到解放軍帽<br />\n甚至到呢排健仔實彈事件<br />\n一件都唔可以算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無論對家有無拆到彈<br />\n我地都應該keep record<br />\n所以希望大家可以集中儲啲核彈喺度<br />\n小至被制服後拳打腳踢 大至健仔件事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我全都要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n方便文宣將來做野<br />\n我地將來清算<br />\n比記者攞返黎用<br />\n所以就算依家連示威都唔夠膽出嘅人<br />\n我唔會怪你 每個人都有自己角色同定位<br />\n請大家可以幫手做條list或者一個合集<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">TLDR</span><br />\n乜事都好 不論大小 請集中呢度po<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa50d75fdadc269bba3395885b7b9fe4e4a2a70f","tid":1630470,"uid":259993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:37:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"86fbd62b62556c1effe417546b17722b8a1c80a9","tid":1630470,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:38:16.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"787d4186c4c3663b5b4738d320950f2b881436e1","tid":1630470,"uid":238467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:39:07.000Z","msg":"721 831 101"},{"pid":"cca74a20ecae87935d9d6dc25f5b0cd33a78faee","tid":1630470,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:39:33.000Z","msg":"開個google share doc 擺晒入去"},{"pid":"8ab0b92450cedcf51a99532a9346a1848dd5eb37","tid":1630470,"uid":238467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:39:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"835440ac8f7a174a7567f18707dc6e330d7844b3","tid":1630470,"uid":238467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"